urance brokersthe company competes with chubb everest re general re corporation hannover re group munich reinsurance company partnerre ltd swiss reinsurance company transatlantic reinsurance company and third point reinsurance ltd » full overview of glbe company address greenlight capital re ltd  market streetsuite  camana baypo box grand cayman     ky p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation david einhorn  simon burton  tim courtis  brendan barry  joseph platt  » more officers  directors greenlight capital re ltd news » more glbe news related topics stocksstock screenerfinancialsreinsurance market research reports greenlight capital re ltd glre  company profile and swot analysis home  contact us  log in   all categories automotive and transportation banking  finance computer  it consumer packaged goods consumer retail electronics  security energy utility and renewable internet manufacturing  industry pharma  healthcare sustainable technology telecom travel  lifestyle advanced search account detail  items in basket order history total  saved searches view basket automotive and transportation automotive and transportation aftermarket commercial vehicles powertrain safety telematics freight logistics  shipping rail intelligent transport systems airway public transport company profiles banking  finance banking  finance retail banking insurance wealth management banking services consumer packaged goods consumer packaged goods food beverages  nonalcoholic personal care beverages  alcoholic household products company profiles computer    it computer    it software cloud computing it services it hardware computer products distribution  support company profiles country overview computing  electronics consumer  retail consumer  retail clothing supermarkets electricals and electronics housekeeping and gardening supplies food and drink specialists company profiles energy utility and renewable energy utility and renewable utilities commodity natura