iated investment approach to maximize book value per share   concentrate our underwriting and investment portfolios on ideas in which we have the highest conviction    vision greenlight re strives to be the most responsive clientfocused reinsurer we make our clients’ success our business belief both our clients and brokers are our partners transparency open communication and trust are paramount to achieving the best possible mutual outcome and maintaining strong longterm partnerships our goals are best achieved through the longterm success of our partners behavior we treat our partners in a manner in which we want to be treated and are respectful of their views and objectives we are collaborative and transparent communicating openly and honestly with the highest levels of integrity we work to resolve issues in an equitable way for all partners goals drive longterm book value growth through profitable underwriting and investing operations   align the interests between all partners in a transaction and our shareholders   be transparent and responsive through a flat organizational structure with a small team of highly skilled underwriters that gives our partners access to decision makers   earn an economic profit on every reinsurance contract and every investment in all market conditions values a collaborative working style that will result in winwin solutions with our partners   committed to our employees by providing training opportunities as well as a challenging and rewarding work environment   committed to our community through supporting charitable organizations and encouraging community involvement our team executive team simon burton chief executive officer sburtongreenlightreky d     m     simon burton joined greenlight re as chief executive officer in july  previously simon served as chief executive officer of sac re ltd from its inception until its sale to hamilton insurance group ltd where he was responsible among other things for building the company’s glo